review_blob:
Tap/growler tall boys Leeds. Very dark colour. Superb citrus fruit aroma. Taste is bitter, hoppy and roasted. One of my favourite beers ever. Exceptional.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

330ml Bottle.
Fantastic Hoppy, Fruity, Bitter IPA. Aroma is Citrus Grapefruit. Perfect balance of bitter and dryness. Excellent. Only slight criticism is that its a bit too drinkable for 7.2% abv!
